{"tid":1463053,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線 有冇人可以教吓我點駁呢段嘢","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:06:11.000Z","uid":140022,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8613f03d0835dde4432ef259708c6e03dd90d0e8","tid":1463053,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"轉發 Via WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n老人家同酒樓經理吹水，經理明顯係撐政府，但老人還未表態，然後經理問老人：「依家學生搞到咁亂點解決好？」<br />\n<br />\n老人淡定說：「送中法無問題，想送中就拎藍色身份証，唔想就拎黃色，第時犯罪藍色就返大陸審，黃色就係香港審，睇下邊個願意返上去囉。」 <br />\n<br />\n最後老人就笑問經理你想拎咩色身份証呀？經理一面尷尬向大家笑一笑，連回答的勇氣都沒有就行開了。 <br />\n<br />\n#我要拎黃色<br />\n<br />\n完全駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4428d4511558eac77e218be8c119066a86b9961","tid":1463053,"uid":44870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"高手在民間"},{"pid":"26c17a115c2ca1817e7eaefd5ffeed7893cb977d","tid":1463053,"uid":305822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:00:25.000Z","msg":"行動po借位求推<br />\n816 經濟制裁 殺人政權(2) (附教學，後面精彩睇曬佢！）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7081a2f41adff1ada4a255b7a5f6f23a5d73080f","tid":1463053,"uid":14404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"但係藍色嘅捉完轉個頭就放喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ec2a869395877e9d6d35907a978babe83c036a","tid":1463053,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7081a2f41adff1ada4a255b7a5f6f23a5d73080f","tid":1463053,"uid":14404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:04:06.000Z","msg":"但係藍色嘅捉完轉個頭就放喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"Sbt<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}